One way is  keep on polling for the Element using Explicit Wait by adding try catch block.

Logic:
                     for(int i=0;i<5;i++)
                    {
                               try{
                                              //find the element;
                                               if element is displayed
                                               break;
                               }
                                catch(Exception e)
                               {

                              }
                          Thread.sleep(1000);
                  }
